# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s24b_2c192be0:

    # "The first few steps inside are sensory overload. A million different sounds and a billion different lights all pour from the sea of slot machines. Even at lunchtime on a Thursday, the majority are occupied."
    "Los primeros pasos adentro son una sobrecarga sensorial. Un millón de sonidos diferentes y mil millones de luces brotan del mar de máquinas tragamonedas. Incluso a la hora del almuerzo un jueves, la mayoría están ocupadas."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s24b_22950d2c:

    # "We both take a second, frozen in place, to try and process it all. This isn’t even my first time in a casino, but I’m overwhelmed just like Marina is."
    "Ambas nos tomamos un segundo, paralizadas, para intentar procesarlo todo. Esta no es ni siquiera mi primera vez en un casino, pero estoy tan abrumada como Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s24b_ce36d8e1:

    # "I can see the reflections of a game in her eyes, like a cartoon character thinking of money."
    "Puedo ver los reflejos de un juego en sus ojos, como un personaje de caricatura pensando en dinero."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s24b_d63ea5e6:

    # Marina "Whoa…"
    Marina "Ваау…"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s24b_3d6a7c09:

    # Amber "Yeah, whoa."
    Amber "Ага, вау."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s24b_8f84bc09:

    # Marina "Is this one of the most popular casinos?"
    Marina "Это одно из самых популярных казино?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s24b_81bcbc3a:

    # Amber "Not even close. Like, it’s big, but it’s not the biggest."
    Amber "Даже не близко. Оно, конечно, большое, но далеко не самое огромное."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f81621fb:

    # Marina "Whoa."
    Marina "Вау."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b027bde5:

    # "I tug her forward."
    "La tiro hacia adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s24b_38f5eedb:

    # Amber "C’mon, we’ll have tons of time to gawk with food in our stomachs."
    Amber "Пойдем, у нас будет тонна времени полюбоваться всем этим, когда мы наконец поедим."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b0f99cc4:

    # "The mention of food steadies her steps."
    "La mención de la comida estabiliza sus pasos."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:80
translate spanish hwb_s24b_8ec405b0:

    # "Giant, overhead signs direct the way to the Buffet. They must be visible from any part of the building."
    "Letreros gigantes en el techo indican el camino al Buffet. Deben ser visibles desde cualquier parte del edificio."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1449d219:

    # "If this place is famous for something besides the food, I don’t know what it is."
    "Si este lugar es famoso por algo además de la comida, no sé qué es."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s24b_734b63e2:

    # "We can smell it before we can see it, even despite the stench of cigarettes and B.O. that are pretty strong here."
    "Podemos olerlo antes de verlo, incluso a pesar del hedor a cigarrillos y sudor que es bastante fuerte aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s24b_e3e9a163:

    # "It doesn’t smell like any one particular food item, but rather lots and lots of them."
    "No huele a ningún alimento en particular, sino a muchos y muchos de ellos."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:88
translate spanish hwb_s24b_565ab85f:

    # "Guided by our stomachs, we half-run towards the buffet."
    "Guiadas por el estómago, medio corremos hacia el bufet."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:90
translate spanish hwb_s24b_e72f2bf0:

    # "The line to get in is small, since we got here so early. Marina hops up and down, trying to peek over the head of the bald guy in front of us."
    "La fila para entrar es pequeña, ya que llegamos tan temprano. Marina brinca de arriba abajo, tratando de asomarse por encima de la cabeza del calvo que está frente a nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:94
translate spanish hwb_s24b_914eb0ed:

    # Amber "Can you see anything?"
    Amber "Видишь что-нибудь?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:98
translate spanish hwb_s24b_6050a052:

    # Marina "Barely. It looks like it goes on forever."
    Marina "Немного. Но кажется, что еды там бесконечное количество."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:102
translate spanish hwb_s24b_27378fad:

    # Amber "Good."
    Amber "Это хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s24b_00c811ca:

    # "I practically throw my card at the attendant. It reminds me of paying to enter an amusement park, and I’m just as excited."
    "Prácticamente le lanzo mi tarjeta al encargado. Me recuerda a pagar para entrar a un parque de diversiones, y estoy igual de emocionada."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:106
translate spanish hwb_s24b_0e1f057a:

    # "We’re let through a small gate and into Heaven."
    "Nos dejan pasar por una pequeña puerta y entramos al Paraíso."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:150
translate spanish hwb_s24b_132fceda:

    # "Rows upon rows of stations form a small maze in the massive room. Deep bins full of food - fried or grilled or baked or roasted - fill nearly every inch of space in each station."
    "Hileras e hileras de estaciones forman un pequeño laberinto en la enorme sala. Bandejas profundas llenas de comida —frita, asada, horneada o rostizada— ocupan casi cada centímetro de espacio en cada estación."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s24b_13678bf4:

    # "Marina and I grab plates from the tall stacks nearby."
    "Marina y yo tomamos platos de las altas pilas cercanas."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s24b_a4a6b1c0:

    # Amber "Meet you in the dining room?"
    Amber "Встретимся в обеденном зале?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s24b_61c25390:

    # "She nods, already distracted, and heads straight for the desserts."
    "Ella asiente, ya distraída, y se dirige directo a los postres."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:170
translate spanish hwb_s24b_bf06afd7:

    # "I load my plate with a slice of prime rib, two rolls, and a scoop of mashed potatoes. I pour gravy over them, letting it run down and soak into everything else."
    "Lleno mi plato con una rebanada de costilla de res, dos panecillos y una cucharada de puré de papas. Les vierto salsa de carne, dejando que se escurra y empape todo lo demás."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s24b_6a84b417:

    # "For good measure, I also throw on a pair of chicken wings from a nearby basket. They’re so fresh that I can see the steam coming off of them."
    "Por si acaso, también añado un par de alitas de pollo de una canasta cercana. Están tan frescas que puedo ver el vapor que sale de ellas."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s24b_c87ae6a2:

    # ". . . I’m gonna need a second plate."
    "... Voy a necesitar un segundo plato."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s24b_8e9cb030:

    # "I grab one off another pile and toss a small piece of salmon, some potstickers from the Asian section, and a large spoonful of some sort of casserole."
    "Tomo uno de otra pila y echo un trozo pequeño de salmón, algunos empanaditas de la sección asiática y una cucharada grande de una especie de cazuela."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s24b_2d720403:

    # "I can’t even guess what it is, but it looks good. Everything looks good."
    "Ni siquiera puedo adivinar qué es, pero se ve bien. Todo se ve bien."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s24b_a8cf1984:

    # "Solely because I can’t fit more food on my plates, I head to the dining area and pick a seat where Marina will be able to find me easily."
    "Solo porque no puedo poner más comida en mis platos, me dirijo al área de comedor y elijo un asiento donde Marina pueda encontrarme fácilmente."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s24b_bdfb44de:

    # "Sure enough, she emerges just a minute later, carrying two plates like I did."
    "Efectivamente, ella aparece apenas un minuto después, cargando dos platos como yo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s24b_66a3b737:

    # Amber "Wow, you weren’t kidding about trying everything."
    Amber "Вау, ты и правда не пошутила, что попробуешь все."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s24b_733b47bd:

    # "Instead of big portions of a few things like I got, Marina has one or two bites of a couple dozen dishes."
    "En lugar de porciones grandes de pocas cosas como yo, Marina tiene uno o dos bocados de un par de docenas de platillos."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s24b_7660d749:

    # "Roughly half of them are cakes or other sweets."
    "Aproximadamente la mitad son pasteles u otros dulces."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1598d6cd:

    # Marina "When in Rome, you know?"
    Marina "Ну знаешь - “Разделяй и властвуй”."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s24b_3b699646:

    # "I slice off a bite of steak and close my eyes in ecstasy while I chew. It’s divine. Holy cow."
    "Corto un bocado de bistec y cierro los ojos en éxtasis mientras mastico. Es divino. Santo cielo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s24b_0858bd28:

    # "Barely balancing her plates as she slides into the seat beside me, Marina bumps against my shoulder as she gets situated, and I almost send a forkful of potatoes into her lap."
    "Apenas equilibrando sus platos mientras se desliza al asiento a mi lado, Marina choca contra mi hombro al acomodarse, y casi mando una cucharada de puré a su regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s24b_34bc7b45:

    # Marina "Whoops, my bad."
    Marina "Упс, мой косяк."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s24b_c4489ad1:

    # "In retaliation, I spear a bite of chicken from her plate, swimming in some Asian sauce."
    "En represalia, ensarto un bocado de pollo de su plato, bañado en alguna salsa asiática."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:213
translate spanish hwb_s24b_9a7a9148:

    # Marina "No fair!"
    Marina "Не честно!"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s24b_741dd744:

    # Amber "It’s double fair."
    Amber "Дважды честно."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f6577a52:

    # Marina "That doesn’t even make sense."
    Marina "Эм... в этой фразе нет никакого смысла."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s24b_42dc6666:

    # "After that, she finally gets to take her first bite. And she melts. Just like me, her eyes roll back into her head while she chews."
    "Después de eso, finalmente logra dar su primer bocado. Y se derrite. Igual que yo, sus ojos se ponen en blanco mientras mastica."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s24b_7650b0a5:

    # Marina "I don’t even remember what this is but it’s amazing.."
    Marina "Я даже не помню, что это, но это великолепно.."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s24b_e01893be:

    # "She scoops up another forkful of what looks like some kind of barbecue brisket and holds it towards me."
    "Toma otra cucharada de lo que parece ser una especie de pechuga de res ahumada y la acerca hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s24b_332258c2:

    # Marina "Try it."
    Marina "Попробуй."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s24b_d541deb0:

    # "I open my mouth and she guides the fork in. I pull back to chew. It’s got a nice, smoky flavor."
    "Abro la boca y ella guía el tenedor hacia adentro. Me retiro para masticar. Tiene un buen sabor ahumado."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s24b_dd2e87a2:

    # Amber "That {i}is{/i} good."
    Amber "{i}Это{/i} очень вкусно."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s24b_ea6447b6:

    # Marina "Right? I almost want to go get a whole plate of just that."
    Marina "Согласна? Мне прям захотелось набрать полную тарелку."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b620f0f3:

    # "Then she tries the baked chicken that she has next to it."
    "Luego prueba el pollo horneado que tiene al lado."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s24b_5e8b1c24:

    # Marina "Wait, never mind, this is even better."
    Marina "Подожди-ка, нет, вот что еще лучше."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1773bdaf:

    # "There’s a distinct lack of vegetables on both of her plates, but she seems to enjoy everything that she got. Every bite results in some statement about how it’s the best thing so far."
    "Hay una notable ausencia de verduras en ambos platos, pero parece disfrutar todo lo que tomó. Cada bocado resulta en alguna declaración sobre cómo es lo mejor hasta ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s24b_2a6d9eb8:

    # Amber "Did you get any of this?"
    Amber "А такое ты пробовала?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s24b_e918ee4f:

    # "I gesture towards the slice of steak that I’ve almost finished."
    "Señalo la rebanada de bistec que casi he terminado."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:257
translate spanish hwb_s24b_741019d8:

    # Marina "Uh uh."
    Marina "Мммм."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s24b_369d3099:

    # Amber "Okay, open up."
    Amber "Ладно, открывай рот."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s24b_945f8691:

    # "She dutifully opens her mouth while I cut a bite for her. It’s the best part; right near the edge where all the flavor is."
    "Obedientemente abre la boca mientras le corto un bocado. Es la mejor parte; justo en el borde donde está todo el sabor."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s24b_22831932:

    # "It’s a little awkward to be feeding her like this, but no one pays any attention to us."
    "Es un poco incómodo darle de comer así, pero nadie nos presta atención."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s24b_3e82ad38:

    # "When she swallows, she sits still."
    "Cuando traga, se queda quieta."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s24b_ac7aa6a6:

    # "Very slowly, she opens her eyes again."
    "Muy lentamente, vuelve a abrir los ojos."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1e4cb95d:

    # Marina "That was literally the best thing I’ve ever eaten."
    Marina "Это было лучшее, что я когда-либо ела."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s24b_75cdec42:

    # Amber "You’ve said that like 20 times so far."
    Amber "Ты так говорила уже раз 20."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s24b_856ab2e8:

    # Marina "I mean it this time! That was illegally good."
    Marina "Я имею в виду, что в этот раз это было до неприличия вкусно."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s24b_0b9828f8:

    # Amber "Now that doesn’t make any sense."
    Amber "Вот теперь - твоя фраза не имеет никакого смысла."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s24b_101de1e1:

    # Marina "It makes double sense!"
    Marina "Это имеет более чем достаточно смысла!"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s24b_73aea83e:

    # "We laugh."
    "Nos reímos."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s24b_51bbe379:

    # Amber "Gramps always used to say that the best place to get a steak was at buffets like this."
    Amber "Дедушка всегда говорил, что если ты хочешь стейк, то нет места лучшего, чем такие буфеты."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:297
translate spanish hwb_s24b_42315698:

    # Amber "Not ‘cause they’re always better, but because you can just go up and get slice after slice."
    Amber "Не потому что они здесь лучшие, а просто потому, что ты можешь их есть кусок за куском."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:299
translate spanish hwb_s24b_fbf6a51c:

    # Amber "Although he’s the only person I’ve met who could eat more than one."
    Amber "Хотя он был единственным человеком кого я знаю, кто мог съесть больше одного стейка."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:301
translate spanish hwb_s24b_832b8c9a:

    # "Marina chuckles with me, but it’s nervous-sounding."
    "Marina se ríe conmigo, pero suena nervioso."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:303
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1d128f58:

    # Amber "I used to tease him for it. No one should be able to eat that much meat!"
    Amber "Я дразнила его за это, ведь человек не должен быть способен съесть столько мяса!"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s24b_1c377f01:

    # Amber "He would always complain about ‘em being too done. He cooked his own steaks to be kinda medium-rare. Closer to rare."
    Amber "Он всегда жаловался, что стейки слишком пережаренные. Сам же он их прожаривал до средней степени. Хотя на деле, он оставлял их практически сырыми."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s24b_516ccc59:

    # Marina "Gross."
    Marina "Фууу."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f1f1ee09:

    # Amber "Don’t tell me you eat yours well done."
    Amber "Только не говори мне, что ты ешь глубоко прожаренные стайки."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s24b_e7c0bba1:

    # Marina "Um…"
    Marina "Эм…"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s24b_a48b17e0:

    # Amber "Marina. I dunno if we can still be together."
    Amber "Марина. Я уже не уверена, что мы сможем быть вместе."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f8001e4f:

    # "She looks pained."
    "Se ve adolorida."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:323
translate spanish hwb_s24b_c974d4d7:

    # Amber "I’m just kidding, you know."
    Amber "Я просто пошутила, ты же понимаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s24b_3fbd411d:

    # Marina "Yeah, I know."
    Marina "Да, я знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s24b_c255ad23:

    # "But it doesn’t sound like it."
    "Pero no suena así."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s24b_220bece0:

    # "I shut up. It’s probably not a good idea to talk about Gramps too much either."
    "Me callo. Probablemente tampoco sea buena idea hablar demasiado del abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s24b_4051b4b0:

    # "Our plates are mostly empty, and I look back at the serving area dubiously."
    "Nuestros platos están casi vacíos, y miro la zona de servicio con desconfianza."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s24b_de022046:

    # Amber "Round two?"
    Amber "Второй раунд?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s24b_41960f93:

    # "She thinks about it, then shakes her head."
    "Lo piensa, luego niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s24b_20e2dfc5:

    # Marina "I think I’d explode if I ate much more."
    Marina "Мне кажется я взорвусь, если съем еще хоть немного."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s24b_8a515515:

    # Amber "Yeah, same."
    Amber "Ага, согласна."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:351
translate spanish hwb_s24b_0e433e25:

    # "There’s a soft flutter against in my cheek as Marina leans over and kisses it."
    "Siento un suave aleteo en mi mejilla cuando Marina se inclina y la besa."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b83e3b17:

    # Marina "Thank you for bringing me."
    Marina "Спасибо, что привезла меня сюда."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:361
translate spanish hwb_s24b_7cdd4106:

    # Amber "Y-Yeah, no problem."
    Amber "Ага, без проблем."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:363
translate spanish hwb_s24b_6c99dc3b:

    # "I intently examine the hard plastic bench I’m sitting on."
    "Examino con atención el banco de plástico duro en el que estoy sentada."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:365
translate spanish hwb_s24b_fd1d1ffd:

    # "Too long passes by before I talk again."
    "Pasa demasiado tiempo antes de que vuelva a hablar."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s24b_2c122d96:

    # Amber "So are you ready to go?"
    Amber "Ну что ты готова идти?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b4ecdd74:

    # Marina "Oh, sure."
    Marina "Ох, да конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s24b_00d4c0b2:

    # "I can tell how on edge she is again."
    "Puedo notar lo tensa que está otra vez."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s24b_b9fc0b55:

    # "Good going, Amber. Nice."
    "Bien hecho, Amber. Genial."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:379
translate spanish hwb_s24b_66675fdd:

    # "I launch to my feet."
    "Me levanto de un salto."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s24b_646f7361:

    # Amber "Just leave the dishes on the table. Someone will come by and clean them up."
    Amber "Просто оставь тарелки на столе. Их потом уберут."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f225a639:

    # "I have no idea if that’s true."
    "No tengo idea de si eso es cierto."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s24b_7dff5164:

    # "I start to leave, expecting Marina to follow me."
    "Empiezo a irme, esperando que Marina me siga."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:392
translate spanish hwb_s24b_037408c8:

    # Marina "Amber!"
    Marina "Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:394
translate spanish hwb_s24b_7f448bf2:

    # "But I turn around. She’s still in the process of getting up."
    "Pero me doy la vuelta. Ella todavía está levantándose."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s24b_26bddd97:

    # Marina "Wait for me."
    Marina "Подожди меня."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s24b_70316400:

    # "First she has to brush her face with a napkin, and then she drains the glass of orange juice she was drinking."
    "Primero tiene que limpiarse la cara con una servilleta, y luego se termina el vaso de jugo de naranja que estaba bebiendo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s24b_075b278e:

    # "Then she scoots out of the booth and hurries toward me."
    "Luego se desliza fuera del reservado y se apresura hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s24b_ffb1c8cc:

    # Marina "Are you alright?"
    Marina "Ты в порядке?"

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:409
translate spanish hwb_s24b_88bdb404:

    # Amber "Yeah, sorry. Just felt kind of nauseous for a second. Probably ate too much."
    Amber "Да, извини. Просто на секунду показалось, что меня затошнило. Наверное, слишком много съела."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s24b_8f7a1145:

    # Marina "Oh."
    Marina "Ох."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:413
translate spanish hwb_s24b_f63c47a4:

    # "I doubt she’s buying it."
    "Dudo que se lo esté creyendo."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s24b_cee768d4:

    # "From the corner of my eye, I see her reach toward my hand. Then she seems to think better of it and lets hers fall back to her side."
    "Por el rabillo del ojo, la veo acercar la mano hacia la mía. Luego parece pensarlo mejor y deja caer la suya a su costado."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s24b_0ab87003:

    # "I grab it myself as I lead the way out of the casino."
    "La tomo yo misma mientras la guío hacia la salida del casino."

# game/script/hwb_s24b.rpy:225
translate spanish hwb_s24b_6a08f5a9:

    # Marina "I don’t even remember what this is but it’s amazing."
    Marina "Я даже не помню, что это, но это великолепно."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s24b.rpy:381
    old "Awkward silence"
    new "Awkward silence"

